  cat <<EOF
${BOLD}Pegasus quickstart${RESET}

The 5 commands you'll use 90% of the time:

  ${BOLD}pegasus new portfolio my-site${RESET}     scaffold a project + open VS Code
  ${BOLD}claude${RESET}                            start Claude Code in any folder
  ${BOLD}opencode${RESET}                          start OpenCode (alternative to Claude)
  ${BOLD}pegasus deploy${RESET}                    ship the current folder live (Surge or GH Pages)
  ${BOLD}pegasus dashboard${RESET}                 visual launcher with everything

The 3 things to do this week:

  1. ${BOLD}pegasus init${RESET}                     fill in your profile (used by skills)
  2. ${BOLD}pegasus signin${RESET}                   log into GitHub, Vercel, Figma
  3. Try a workflow:               ${BOLD}cat ~/.pegasus/templates/auto-mode/workflows.md${RESET}

When stuck:

  ${BOLD}pegasus doctor${RESET}                    diagnose your install
  ${BOLD}pegasus test${RESET}                      end-to-end verification
  ${BOLD}pegasus help${RESET}                      all commands
  ${BOLD}pegasus open troubleshooting${RESET}      open TROUBLESHOOTING.md
EOF
}

cmd_stats() {
  cat <<EOF
${BOLD}Pegasus stats${RESET}

  Skills installed:    $(ls -d "$HOME/.claude/skills"/*/ 2>/dev/null | wc -l | tr -d ' ')
  Templates installed: $(ls -d "$PEGASUS_HOME/templates"/*/ 2>/dev/null | wc -l | tr -d ' ')
  Projects:            $(ls -d "$PROJECTS_DIR"/*/ 2>/dev/null | wc -l | tr -d ' ')
  Cheatsheets:         $(ls "$PROJECTS_DIR"/*.md 2>/dev/null | wc -l | tr -d ' ')

For activity stats (copies, weekly, streaks), open the dashboard:
  ${BOLD}pegasus dashboard${RESET}  →  scroll to "Your Pulse"
